    'from' => 'Eris Reddoch',
    'body' => 'On 10/09/96 at 06:30 PM,  Paul Walker <tiger@datasync.com> said:

>>I\'m toying with using the following: Attribute + (Aptitude*Skill) =
>>Target Number

