    'body' => 'David Joseph Smart <dsmart@flash.net> pointed out that

>> > Jump capable ships have a Zuchai crystal grid in the hull. This grid is

was wrong, i.e.

>grid is made of lanthanum. The zuchai crystals are used as an energy
